  "general_provisions": "This bill addresses the manner in which a candidate's name may appear on a ballot. ",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>establishes criteria for permitting a candidate to:<hr><ltbullet1>use the candidate's middle name instead of the candidate's first name on a ballot;<hr><ltbullet1>use the candidate's nickname on a ballot; or<hr><ltbullet1>use the candidate's initial on a ballot;<hr><ltbullet>establishes a procedure for a candidate to request that the candidate's name appear on a ballot as described in the preceding paragraph; and<hr><ltbullet>provides for an appeal of a rejection of a request described in the preceding paragraph.  ",
